Class Tier2Employee

java.lang.Object
Person
Employee
Tier2Employee
All Implemented Interfaces:
Printable
public class Tier2Employee extends Employee
Represents a Tier 2 employee, extending the Employee class with additional information such as the employee's certification. Tier 2 employees handle advanced tasks that require specific certifications.
Since:
2024-11-19
Version:
